{"id": 1319, "genre": 1001, "title": "你在做家务这件事上有哪些偏执？", "description": "你干，我不干。（题图来自：Mike Ellis）", "record_count": 5208, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20161107164639Ut04aGYEmxqplOMw.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-11-16T03:00:36Z", "options": [{"id": 134416, "content": "一定要把边边角角打扫干净！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 515073}, {"id": 134418, "content": "要么不干，要么追求完美", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 816724}, {"id": 134441, "content": "一旦开始就非常强迫症，总想收拾干净又无比烦躁", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 835558}, {"id": 134442, "content": "东西不肯扔，总认定它会有有用的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 739299}, {"id": 134401, "content": "做都做了，一思思不干净都觉得实在挑衅，本来只想拖个地，却把柜子，架子都收拾了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 819487}, {"id": 174596, "content": "平时不打扫，心情不好或特别好的时候才会打扫", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 957785}, {"id": 134661, "content": "看到乱七八糟的东西就浑身难受！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 100919}, {"id": 134407, "content": "可以洗碗洗马桶整理杂物，但就不乐意拖地:(", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 819158}, {"id": 151559, "content": "要么我全包了，要么我不插手！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 895036}, {"id": 134409, "content": "千万不要中途打断我………", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 835492}, {"id": 134665, "content": "只喜欢做饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 835452}, {"id": 134411, "content": "收拾东西就要像玩华容道一样，要摆的严丝合缝才行", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 788070}, {"id": 138251, "content": "什么是做家务", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 776389}, {"id": 134412, "content": "一定会扔东西，扔很多。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 835472}, {"id": 134415, "content": "洗锅碗时，锅跟碗一定要分开洗，如果放在一起就会莫名其妙烦躁?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 828638}, {"id": 134671, "content": "music", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 836754}, {"id": 134417, "content": "大扫除的话地上没有一根头发，所有物品衣服都要归位 所有穿过一次的衣服必须全洗 要看着视频或者听着音乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 835506}, {"id": 134419, "content": "一定要放蜡笔小新\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 835511}, {"id": 134421, "content": "等想起来做家务  一定要好天气  开着熟悉的电视剧做背景音  慢慢收拾不着急", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 285984}, {"id": 135189, "content": "一定要好好找个下午把该干的都干了，b\n不扔点东西也很不爽。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 839386}, {"id": 134422, "content": "心情好就干，没心情就不干，很随意，除非脏的看不下去", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 835516}, {"id": 134423, "content": "我想干的时候干的热火朝天，不想干的时候驴拉我都拉不动", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 88756}, {"id": 135959, "content": "地上不可以有一根头发", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 840921}, {"id": 134426, "content": "要么不收拾，一收拾就像搬了新家一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 835145}, {"id": 134427, "content": "只要是不沾水的家务都成，单身狗怕水", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 810969}, {"id": 134683, "content": "拖地一定要开空调", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 836841}, {"id": 134174, "content": "一定要有BGM", "image": null, "praise_count": 913, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 167600}, {"id": 134175, "content": "还好吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 834885}, {"id": 135199, "content": "洗碗绝对不主动扔垃圾", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 839412}, {"id": 134176, "content": "攒一堆再一起干掉真的莫名的爽", "image": null, "praise_count": 229, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 658145}, {"id": 134432, "content": "不爱被强迫干高频率的反复整理家里的所有物品，其他家务都可以", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 835068}, {"id": 134177, "content": "一旦开始打扫，就要彻底（如果木地板可以掀起来就好了！）", "image": null, "praise_count": 542, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 233800}, {"id": 134178, "content": "家务劳动家人一起做", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 834963}, {"id": 135458, "content": "边唱歌边家务，扫地拖地都带感", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 713409}, {"id": 134179, "content": "一定要有电视肥皂剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 770443}, {"id": 134435, "content": "脏了五天干净了两天", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 741469}, {"id": 134180, "content": "一定要没人在的时候，放着音乐来", "image": null, "praise_count": 434, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 833844}, {"id": 134436, "content": "衣服攒到一堆再洗\n打扫自己屋子开始渐渐延伸到整个家\n\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 835540}, {"id": 134181, "content": "要不就不干 要不就360度无死角的全都要清理一遍", "image": null, "praise_count": 725, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 800401}, {"id": 134437, "content": "有朋自远方来 不亦忙乎", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 782690}, {"id": 135973, "content": "家里必须没有人～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 841613}, {"id": 134182, "content": "一定要熨烫床单被罩枕巾…", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 783415}, {"id": 134438, "content": "看不到摸不到的地方绝对不打扫。?", "image": "img/option/option/201611162048196KNjvu7Qp43nt2Dm.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 817661}, {"id": 161574, "content": "不喜欢晾衣服和叠衣服", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 924772}, {"id": 134183, "content": "非常讨厌淘米，为了逃避淘米，可以刷一礼拜厕所", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118131}, {"id": 134439, "content": "要么不打扫，要么打扫得干干净净，不允许有任何污渍", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 600837}, {"id": 134184, "content": "非常喜欢刷厕所，刷白了超有成就感", "image": null, "praise_count": 40, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118131}, {"id": 134440, "content": "因为做家务，我看了不下百遍武林外传！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 786495}, {"id": 134185, "content": "不会⋯⋯我错了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 273191}, {"id": 134186, "content": "只喜欢做饭不喜欢洗碗", "image": null, "praise_count": 90, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 834969}]}